sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant API
    participant Database

    Client->>API: GET /carts/{cartId}
    API->>Database: SELECT id, created_at, updated_at FROM carts WHERE id = $1
    Database-->>API: carts row (or not found)
    alt cart not found
        API-->>Client: 404 Not Found (ProblemDetail)
    else cart found
        API->>Database: SELECT id, cart_id, product_id, quantity, unit_price, created_at, updated_at FROM cart_items WHERE cart_id = $1
        Database-->>API: cart_items rows
        API-->>Client: 200 OK (Cart with items)
    end
